ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX ashrae: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\n\\nSELECT ?property ?alcEndpoint ?mpcEndpoint WHERE {\\n  # Property must be a type of observable/actuatable property\\n  ?property a ?propClass .\\n  FILTER(?propClass IN (\\n    ashrae:QuantifiableObservableProperty,\\n    ashrae:EnumeratedObservableProperty,\\n    ashrae:QuantifiableActuatableProperty,\\n    ashrae:EnumeratedActuatableProperty,\\n    ashrae:TemperatureSetpoint,\\n    ashrae:PercentCommand\\n  ))\\n  \\n  # The property is linked to a Zone via hasProperty\\n  ?zone a ashrae:Zone .\\n  ?zone ashrae:hasProperty ?property .\\n  \\n  # Retrieve the ALc (endpoint) and MPC (mpc_db_name) values\\n  ?property brick:endpoint ?alcEndpoint .\\n  ?property brick:mpc_db_name ?mpcEndpoint .\\n  \\n  # Property is not editable  either writable is false or not present\\n  OPTIONAL { ?property brick:writable ?writable . }\\n  FILTER( !bound(?writable) || ?writable = false )\\n}\\nORDER BY ?property\\nLIMIT 100""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 4, 36, 57, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')
